Kirinyaga Woman Representative Wangui Ngirici has apologised following a video doing the rounds showing her overlap and then confront a passenger on the right side of the road. Ngirici on Tuesday said she made a mistake and accepted correction. The legislator and the motorist are seen in the video arguing as the man scolds her for driving on the wrong side of the road. The motorist is heard in the clip asking the woman representative to adhere to road rules. "Follow the rules. You are a grown woman, " the man said.